com/p/DY4Fh86tCkp/", "caption": "You know that feeling of disconnect that sometimes comes with your home? Maybe you\u2019ve cleaned for hours and it still doesn\u2019t sit quite right, something feels a bit off (but your can\u2019t quite put your finger on it?) Well I have a theory. \nI think it is really tempting to see lovely things around us, in the media, on socials or even in your best friend\u2019s house and for us to love it and then try and copy and paste that into out own life and home. But it never really works (or hardly ever) and I think this is because that effort is going into the aesthetics rather than the feeling. \nDoes that make sense? I found a lot more peace with my home when I started to ask myself how I wanted it to feel, rather than look, when I put the feeling first the aesthetics naturally fell into place and it started to feel mine and \u2018right\u2019. Just a theory but a potential one to think about if your home always feels bit \u2018off\u2019 and you are not sure why. Gem xxxx", "timestamp": "2026-05-28T08:54:15.000Z", "videoDuration": 5.431, "videoPlayCount": 11077, "videoViewCount": 1985, "likesCount": -1, "commentsCount": 2, "displayUrl": "https://scontent-atl3-2.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/708068849_18439268902142472_8624698969978715729_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&_nc_ht=scontent-atl3-2.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=100&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gFd_yNCs5xabgsmRl-JnUEuzUE6bifgylbtlHkxCSWZQCT70ULabuk2npXVakApqPE&_nc_ohc=YgrrdQwE5-8Q7kNvwGpEJPt&_nc_gid=m67UgJDr_gzvo5sO3NU5aw&edm=APs17CUBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af_JXX0bbOuPBnij4G6flrOnijc9Qv2_5W9aJ73sSHMs0Q&oe=6A312DB0&_nc_sid=10d13b", "videoUrl": "https://scontent-atl3-1.cdninstagram.com/o1/v/t16/f2/m86/AQP5XIsyYFU_mlMe-yNuC4_06qc-BYQgmklwFhXGPU0MwcX-h4gZDvv9BcaW8P9uEh0LQIkj7Xg2FcNHZ9EKpIvAB8wdGoFq2nnxxcM.mp4?stp=dst-mp4&efg=eyJxZV9ncm91cHMiOiJbXCJpZ193ZWJfZGVsaXZlcnlfdnRzX290ZlwiXSIsInZlbmNvZGVfdGFnIjoidnRzX3ZvZF91cmxnZW4uY2xpcHMuYzIuNzIwLmJhc2VsaW5lIn0&_nc_cat=106&vs=1547476390077078_2147891453&_nc_vs=HBksFQIYUmlnX3hwdl9yZWVsc19wZXJtYW5lbnRfc3JfcHJvZC8zRTQ4N0QwRkI3NjI0QjdFMzY1NTA0RDg3NkEzMUU5OV92aWRlb19kYXNoaW5pdC5tcDQVAALIARIAFQIYUWlnX3hwdl9wbGFjZW1lbnRfcGVybWFuZW50X3YyLzUyNDI4MjQzMDBEMEU3OEIxOEY5RDk2QUM5RDg0MEFBX2F1ZGlvX2Rhc2hpbml0Lm1wNBUCAsgBEgAoABgAGwAVAAAmitrX0%2FvavwUVAigCQzMsF0AVmZmZmZmaGBJkYXNoX2Jhc2VsaW5lXzFfdjERAHX%2BB2XmnQEA&_nc_rid=fa63f387f8&ccb=9-4&oh=00_Af_CPj8ydzuKXU-tVI-9ARwhqnjODLq8KQ7uvxpsm2Wdmw&oe=6A2D42CE&_nc_sid=10d13b", "musicInfo": {"artist_name": "dennisivnvc, Dani Catal\u00e1", "song_name": "Sitting in the Grass", "uses_original_audio": false, "should_mute_audio": false, "should_mute_audio_reason": "", "audio_id": "2126996827751138"}, "ownerUsername": "the_organised_mum", "ownerFullName": "Gemma Bray Founder of TOM"}, {"shortCode": "DYpjbZTNYgk", "url": "https://www.instagram.com/p/DYpjbZTNYgk/", "caption": "Oven Baked Chorizo Potatoes \u2b07\ufe0f This is a firm fave in our house, it goes with anything and tbh is even great on its own \ud83d\ude0d. \nI always kind of eyeball this one \u2026\nPan fry chopped chorizo in a pan that is both hob and oven proof. \nRoughly chop your potatoes (I leave the skin on) and put them in the same pan as your chorizo, pour over enough stock to just about cover the amount of potatoes you are using and bring to the boil. I added some tomato pur\u00e9e to the stock in this one. Season. \nCover and then pop in the oven at about 180 degrees for roughly 45/50 mins. Enjoy \ud83d\ude0d", "timestamp": "2026-05-22T17:36:22.000Z", "videoDuration": 16.043, "videoPlayCount": 15846, "videoViewCount": 4196, "likesCount": -1, "commentsCount": 0, "displayUrl": "https://scontent-lga3-2.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/703811993_18438293161142472_7612397347039701150_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&_nc_ht=scontent-lga3-2.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=100&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gHlNU8YP8W6L0CbfuRhmdBQsM5RfKRLP6VJ6Cqh_zq4G4GV4NMZEpHFRGwKFteYirQ&_nc_ohc=tMZK0WuwewEQ7kNvwHGaNYv&_nc_gid=YZL49qQZPS6u8cs4U9HSYA&edm=APs17CUBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af-KPiDiD2BhSpK4FH49T-vPngA2uYxSI4qy3QWUDDcmRA&oe=6A3134CD&_nc_sid=10d13b", "videoUrl": "https://scontent-lga3-1.cdninstagram.com/o1/v/t16/f2/m86/AQNHXURfjw2XR53a30XqcEHqjNW184BvPyiq_HMt8D91FlyOwA4XLXzGkSpwmxPj-457OEYr57gfUCazZG1czXaxjfnM5tyORukWYCA.mp4?stp=dst-mp4&efg=eyJxZV9ncm91cHMiOiJbXCJpZ193ZWJfZGVsaXZlcnlfdnRzX290ZlwiXSIsInZlbmNvZGVfdGFnIjoidnRzX3ZvZF91cmxnZW4uY2xpcHMuYzIuNzIwLmJhc2VsaW5lIn0&_nc_cat=103&vs=2026771827872572_39439611&_nc_%2BB2XmnQEA&_nc_rid=1abb186fd0&ccb=9-4&oh=00_Af-wkgsAVK7tVbf7P2e0P37R5op2YGBq8p1B1tOnp8fnJw&oe=6A2D4F89&_nc_sid=10d13b", "musicInfo": {"artist_name": "the_organised_mum", "song_name": "Original audio", "uses_original_audio": true, "should_mute_audio": false, "should_mute_audio_reason": "", "audio_id": "28249348114655882"}, "ownerUsername": "the_organised_mum", "ownerFullName": "Gemma Bray Founder of TOM"}, {"shortCode": "DYeDOKfthkH", "url": "https://www.instagram.com/p/DYeDOKfthkH/", "caption": "The fantasy of stopping. Putting the vacuum down and walking away.. \n\nIf you do find yourself indulging in this little fantasy more times than you would like to admit then just to reassure you\u2026You\u2019re thinking about it because your competence has made your work invisible. The better you got at holding it all together, the more it became yours to do. \n\nNobody notices the effort because you, my love, are a victim of your own success. \n\nFifteen thousand times a day you think about stopping, and fifteen thousand times a day you don\u2019t. Because somehow watching it fall apart feels worse than just doing it yourself.\n\nLove you, Gem x", "timestamp": "2026-05-18T06:14:44.000Z", "videoDuration": 7.336, "videoPlayCount": 37191, "videoViewCount": 17758, "likesCount": 215, "commentsCount": 4, "displayUrl": "https://instagram.ffcm1-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t51.71878-15/687376376_975151221920047_6617080697017908682_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&_nc_ht=instagram.ffcm1-2.fna.fbcdn.net&_nc_cat=107&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gHw43JZ-CWuiHAg-_LS3umZv0u3SP8slAVoMjhhtBcJLdiKvDOh390Wk8vQnFHepMxoZvywDLAbq3o87XSHqHa3&_nc_ohc=zPXyO15ZKw0Q7kNvwGKflpc&_nc_gid=w0CWo02acnvHcVpS2GeGtA&edm=APs17CUBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af8u0sa8gozoHR_pXuYOYhjl_Zi7BTkScT4dwnzGN89HVA&oe=6A3140A3&_nc_sid=10d13b", "videoUrl": "https://instagram.ffcm1-2.fna.fbcdn.net/o1/v/t16/f2/m86/AQP4Rp2G0PkzN1yYFbLS8RmLF3NkrUWqbpZ1T5UdGNt8625DPZO1VGih8VU8Ad_yXMbw3OL3azFtVCJ8sV2P2DMbhHMKc-1p3gq_ivQ.mp4?stp=dst-mp4&efg=eyJxZV9ncm91cHMiOiJbXCJpZ193ZWJfZGVsaXZlcnlfdnRzX290ZlwiXSIsInZlbmNvZGVfdGFnIjoidnRzX3ZvZF91cmxnZW4uY2xpcHMuYzIuNzIwLmJhc2VsaW5lIn0&_nc_cat=101&vs=2817485728584182_505333689&_nc_%2BB2XmnQEA&_nc_rid=2f68630874&ccb=9-4&oh=00_Af_jWqNW4R2zRc_1jgj3IfHtsv_5Gtsr2NTl7knbM85Lcg&oe=6A2D511C&_nc_sid=10d13b", "musicInfo": {"artist_name": "the_organised_mum", "song_name": "Original audio", "uses_original_audio": true, "should_mute_audio": false, "should_mute_audio_reason": "", "audio_id": "27797156929871297"}, "ownerUsername": "the_organised_mum", "ownerFullName": "Gemma Bray Founder of TOM"}, {"shortCode": "DYXTuW3N-bp", "url": "https://www.instagram.com/p/DYXTuW3N-bp/", "caption": "It\u2019s so easy to default to blaming ourselves isn\u2019t it? \u2018I\u2019m not working harder enough/I need to be more xyz/ I should just xyz\u2019. When I was younger I always thought the answer was that I needed to fix myself and try harder. But I can hand on heart say that never really worked and things became so much easier and my mind became so much clearer when I accepted that I am just one woman, with a finite amount of energy and time and all I can ever do is my best with what I have xxxxx", "timestamp": "2026-05-15T15:28:38.000Z", "videoDuration": 7.547, "videoPlayCount": 42872, "videoViewCount": 18540, "likesCount": -1, "commentsCount": 2, "displayUrl": "https://scontent-hou1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/692509508_1490707636401781_1467501098363442283_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&_nc_ht=scontent-hou1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=101&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gFCKDzwBGMR6cU9Qx0RuBk3MM